<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IM退款自助化-免费取消场景</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f0f2f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; }
        .phone-mockup { width: 375px; height: 720px; background: #ededed; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; border: 8px solid #333; border-radius: 32px; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
        .chat-area { flex: 1; padding: 12px; overflow-y: auto; scrollbar-width: none; }
        .chat-area::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
        .card-shadow { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        .btn-active:active { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(0.96); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="p-8">

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span> 房客端 (免费取消)
            </h2>
            <div class="phone-mockup relative text-left">
                <div class="bg-[#f7f7f7] p-4 flex items-center border-b border-gray-200">
                    <div class="w-7 h-7 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white font-bold">房东</div>
                    <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs">美团民宿房东</div>
                </div>

                <div class="chat-area">
                    <div class="flex justify-end mb-4">
                        <div class="bg-[#ffda00] text-gray-800 p-2.5 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-[75%] text-[13px]">去不了了，能取消订单吗</div>
                        <div class="w-7 h-7 bg-orange-400 rounded-full ml-2 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">客</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex justify-start mb-4 text-left">
                        <div class="w-7 h-7 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-full mr-2 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-orange-500 font-bold flex-shrink-0">美</div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl w-[300px] card-shadow border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="p-3 flex bg-gray-50/50 border-b border-gray-50">
                                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden text-left">
                                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?w=200&h=200&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-3 flex-1">
                                    <div class="font-bold text-[13px] text-gray-800 mb-1">釜子锅的测试房</div>
                                    <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">10.10－10.15 | 合计 ¥139</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
                                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-[14px]">免费取消</span>
                                    <span class="text-blue-500 text-[10px]">查看政策 ></span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mb-3">取消将原路退还 ¥139.00</p>
                                <div class="mt-2 bg-blue-50/50 p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-blue-100/30 italic text-blue-800 text-[10px] leading-relaxed">
                                    💡 温馨提示：好房机不可失，当前价格已锁定，取消后可能无法享有哦
                                </div>
                                <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
                                    <button class="w-full bg-[#ffda00] py-2.5 rounded-lg text-[12px] font-bold btn-active">继续入住</button>
                                    <button class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 py-2 rounded-lg text-[11px] btn-active">免费取消订单</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 flex items-center">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-orange-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span> 房东端 (镜像视图)
            </h2>
            <div class="phone-mockup relative">
                <div class="bg-[#f7f7f7] p-4 flex items-center border-b border-gray-200">
                    <div class="w-7 h-7 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-2 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white font-bold">客</div>
                    <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-xs text-left leading-tight">美团民宿房客</div>
                </div>

                <div class="chat-area flex flex-col">
                    <div class="flex justify-start mb-4">
                        <div class="w-7 h-7 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-2 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] text-white font-bold flex-shrink-0">客</div>
                        <div class="bg-white text-gray-800 p-2.5 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none text-[13px] shadow-sm italic text-left">能退吗？临时去不了了</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex justify-end mb-4">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl w-[300px] overflow-hidden card-shadow border border-gray-100 mr-2 text-left">
                            <div class="p-3 flex bg-gray-50/50 border-b border-gray-50">
                                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden text-left">
                                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?w=200&h=200&fit=crop" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
                                </div>
                                <div class="ml-3 flex-1">
                                    <div class="font-bold text-[13px] text-gray-800 mb-1">釜子锅的测试房</div>
                                    <div class="text-[11px] text-gray-500">10.10－10.15 | 合计 ¥139</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-1">
                                    <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-[14px]">免费取消</span>
                                    <span class="text-blue-500 text-[10px]">查看政策 ></span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mb-3">取消将原路退还 ¥139.00</p>
                                <div class="mt-2 bg-blue-50/30 p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-blue-100/20 italic text-blue-800 text-[9px] leading-relaxed">
                                    💡 温馨提示：好房机不可失，当前价格已锁定，取消后可能无法享有哦
                                  <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
                                    <button class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 py-2 rounded-lg text-[11px] btn-active">继续入住</button>
                                    <button class="w-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-400 py-2 rounded-lg text-[11px] btn-active">免费取消订单</button>
